  "thag11.1:0.2": "",
  "thag11.1:0.3": "",
  "thag11.1:0.4": "",
  "thag11.1:1.1": "What do you want in the woods, my boy,",
  "thag11.1:1.2": "like a bird exposed to the rain?",
  "thag11.1:1.3": "Monsoons refresh you,",
  "thag11.1:1.4": "for seclusion is for those in jhāna.",
  "thag11.1:2.1": "As the monsoon wind",
  "thag11.1:2.2": "drives the clouds in the rainy season,",
  "thag11.1:2.3": "so thoughts concerned with seclusion",
  "thag11.1:2.4": "impel me. * * *",
  "thag11.1:3.1": "A black crow",
  "thag11.1:3.2": "making its home in a charnel ground",
  "thag11.1:3.3": "inspires within me mindfulness in—",
  "thag11.1:3.4": "based on dispassion for— the body. * * *",
  "thag11.1:4.1": "One whom others don’t guard,",
  "thag11.1:4.2": "who doesn’t guard others:",
  "thag11.1:4.3": "He is a monk who lies down in ease,",
  "thag11.1:4.4": "unconcerned with sensual passions. * * *",
  "thag11.1:5.1": "With clear waters & massive boulders,",
  "thag11.1:5.2": "frequented by monkeys & deer,",
  "thag11.1:5.3": "covered with moss & water weeds:",
  "thag11.1:5.4": "Those rocky crags refresh me. * * *",
  "thag11.1:6.1": "I’ve lived in wildernesses,",
  "thag11.1:6.2": "canyons, & caves,",
  "thag11.1:6.3": "isolated dwellings",
  "thag11.1:6.4": "frequented by predator & prey, but never have I known an ignoble, aversive resolve:",
  "thag11.1:7.1": "“May these beings be destroyed, be slaughtered,",
  "thag11.1:7.2": "fall into pain.” * * *",
  "thag11.1:7.3": "",
  "thag11.1:7.4": "",
  "thag11.1:8.1": "The Teacher has been served by me;",
  "thag11.1:8.2": "the Awakened One’s bidding, done;",
  "thag11.1:8.3": "the heavy load, laid down;",
  "thag11.1:8.4": "the guide to becoming, uprooted.",
  "thag11.1:9.1": "And the goal for which I went forth",
  "thag11.1:9.2": "from home life into homelessness",
  "thag11.1:9.3": "I’ve reached:",
  "thag11.1:9.4": "the end of all fetters.",
  "thag11.1:10.1": "I don’t delight in death,",
  "thag11.1:10.2": "don’t delight in living.",
  "thag11.1:10.3": "I await my time",
  "thag11.1:10.4": "as a worker his wage.",
  "thag11.1:11.1": "I don’t delight in death,",
  "thag11.1:11.2": "don’t delight in living.",
  "thag11.1:11.3": "I await my time,",
  "thag11.1:11.4": "mindful, alert.",
  "thag11.1:11.5": "",
  "thag11.1:11.6": "",
  "thag11.1:12.0": "",
